## 5. Component Categories (Atomic Design)

Based on the UX specifications in `/Users/anotonio.silva/antonio/llm-harness/docs/ux/` and types in `/Users/anotonio.silva/antonio/llm-harness/src/mileage/types/`:

### 5.1 Atoms (Smallest Units)

| Component | Description | Variants | Props Source |
|-----------|-------------|----------|--------------|
| StatusChip | Train/maintenance status indicator | FIT, RESTRICTED, UNFIT, IN_SERVICE, etc. | `FitnessStatus`, `TrainStatus` |
| Badge | Numeric count indicator | Default, Warning, Critical | `AlertPriority` |
| ProgressBar | PM window progress | SAFE, APPROACHING, CRITICAL, OVERDUE | `PMWindowStatus` |
| TrendIndicator | Up/down/stable arrow | Up (green), Down (red), Stable (gray) | `TrendDirection` |
| Icon | Fleet and status icons | Kinki Sharyo, Alstom, PM levels | `FleetType`, `PMLevel` |
| Spinner | Loading state | Small, Medium, Large | - |
| Skeleton | Loading placeholder | Text, Card, Row, Chart | - |

### 5.2 Molecules (Combinations of Atoms)

| Component | Description | Key Features | Types Reference |
|-----------|-------------|--------------|-----------------|
| KPICard | Key performance indicator | Value, trend, threshold states | `KPICardData` (dashboard.ts) |
| AlertItem | Alert/notification item | Priority, category, actions | `DashboardAlert` (dashboard.ts) |
| FilterPill | Active filter indicator | Label, removable | `FilterChip` (train-grid.ts) |
| TrainCard | Mobile train summary | Status, mileage, PM window | `TrainGridRow` (train-grid.ts) |
| PMMarker | Timeline PM marker | Level, status, date | `PMTimelineMarker` (dashboard.ts) |
| ToastNotification | Transient notification | Priority, auto-dismiss | `Toast` (notification-ui.ts) |
| ScoreBreakdown | AI recommendation score | Fitness, mileage, PM distance | `ScoreBreakdown` (run-assignment-ui.ts) |

### 5.3 Organisms (Complex Components)

| Component | Description | Key Features | Types Reference |
|-----------|-------------|--------------|-----------------|
| TrainMileageGrid | 128-train data table | Virtual scroll, sorting, filtering | `TrainGridState` (train-grid.ts) |
| FleetStatusPanel | Fleet summary with donut | Status distribution, PM due counts | `FleetStatusSummary` (dashboard.ts) |
| ManHourChart | Area/line combination chart | Gap analysis, comparison modes | `ManHourChartConfig` (man-hour-chart.ts) |
| PMTimeline | Maintenance schedule timeline | Zoom levels, status markers | `TimelineConfig` (dashboard.ts) |
| NotificationCenter | Alert inbox | Tabs, grouping, actions | `NotificationCenterState` (notification-ui.ts) |
| FilterToolbar | Multi-filter controls | Fleet, status, PM due, search | `TrainGridFilters` (train-grid.ts) |
| RunAssignmentBoard | Drag-and-drop assignments | Train pool, route slots, AI suggestions | `DailyScheduleViewState` (run-assignment-ui.ts) |
| ComparisonPanel | Scenario comparison | Side-by-side, overlay, table | `ComparisonViewState` (scenario-ui.ts) |

### 5.4 Templates (Page Layouts)

| Template | Description | Child Regions |
|----------|-------------|---------------|
| DashboardLayout | Main dashboard structure | Header, KPI row, 2-column grid, footer |
| GridLayout | Data table pages | Toolbar, table, pagination, bulk actions |
| FormLayout | Settings/configuration | Sidebar nav, form sections, save actions |
| SidebarLayout | Detail views | Sidebar navigation, main content, actions |
| ModalLayout | Dialogs and modals | Header, body, footer actions |

### 5.5 Pages (Full Screens)

| Page | Description | Key Components |
|------|-------------|----------------|
| Dashboard | Main entry point | KPICards, FleetStatusPanel, PMTimeline, AlertsPanel |
| FleetStatus | Train mileage grid | FilterToolbar, TrainMileageGrid, BulkActions |
| Maintenance | PM scheduling | PMTimeline, ResourceChart, ScheduleTable |
| RunAssignments | Daily allocations | RunAssignmentBoard, WeeklyPlanner |
